<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 22:09:23 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0a3c8fd04da</link><description>&lt;p&gt;行业工具&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A black and white photo of a drum set with symbols and sticks." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a0a3c8fd04da.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 22:09:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0a224182f5d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;轨道&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Train rails in a railway station. " height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a0a224182f5d.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 20:17:07 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0a02b01fc72</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一张俯拍的旅行插头适配器照片，两个都贴着标签，放在浅色木桌上。左边是一款哑光黑色适配器，带有英式插头的三根黄铜插脚。一张带横幅边框的白色标签包裹在适配器上，用无衬线字体写着"Kingdom of Brexitopia"。右边是一款白色适配器，带有美式插头的两个平行扁平插脚和一个圆形接地插脚。它配有一个同样带横幅边框的白色标签，上面写着"'murica"。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A top-down photograph of two labeled travel plug adapters resting on a light-colored wooden table.
On the left is a matte black adapter featuring the three-pronged brass pins of a UK plug. A white label with a banner border is wrapped around it, reading &amp;quot;Kingdom of Brexitopia&amp;quot; in a sans-serif font.
On the right is a white adapter featuring the two flat parallel pins and one round ground pin of a US plug. It has a matching white label with a banner border that reads &amp;quot;'murica&amp;quot;." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mangochutney/6a0a02b01fc72.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mangochutney.some.pics"&gt;@mangochutney&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 18:03:34 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>终于读完系列佳作</title><link>https://some.pics/6a09f871274de</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我有点羞愧地承认，从去年12月初到现在才终于读完这一本。有了孩子之后很难抽出时间，不过我仍然会给他们读其他书。

这真是一套非常出色的系列。

现在开始读《Auberon》中篇小说了！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Screencap of the Bookmory application on Android. Shows the seventh book of The Expanse series, Persepolis Rising, by James S A Corey. The first reading has been completed." height="879" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/swrogers/6a09f871274de.jpg" width="1439"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://swrogers.some.pics"&gt;@swrogers&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 17:18:43 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a09d58950276</link><description>&lt;p&gt;褐矢嘲鸫&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Brown bird in green grass looking into thicker foilage" height="2304" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/chrisod/6a09d58950276.jpg" width="3072"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://chrisod.some.pics"&gt;@chrisod&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 14:49:48 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>